'''New Alderaan''' was a radical political group of [[Alderaanian/Legends|Alderaanians]] who had survived the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|Destruction of Alderaan]]. They viewed [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] as a hero and advocated the murder of all [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] involved in the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] destruction, including [[Qwi Xux]].

